1. foward the invite to the mentor (when you recieve the EIT review invite)
2. do the dry run with your mentor (presentation preparation with the mentor, to check what is missing, e.t.c)
3. Start writing the TR report 
4. Ensure everything that you do meet the ECSA 11 outcomes
5. Ensure you build your compitence i.e. working with complex projects.
6. We can have virtual site visit where mentors use Whatsapp videos to share what is happening on site.
7. Lebo wil share the slide with outcomes and responsibility level on the next invite. 
8. Don't go deep to explain the project. Talk about your individual contribution to the project. 
9. Everyone must have their mentor on the next meeting.